---
title: Seared Serrano Steak with Sweet Mango Slaw & Cilantro Rice
description: A mix of balsamic vinegar, garlic, and serrano pepper makes for a sweet, spicy, and tangy steak marinade. For a hit of brightness, we’ve paired juicy mango with red onion and lime for subtly sweet side slaw. Classic cilantro-lime rice is the perfect base to soak up all those flavors!
